Class SGDStreamingInitialRoundIterator

    Iterator<SGDObjectiveTerm>, StreamingIterator<SGDObjectiveTerm>

    public class SGDStreamingInitialRoundIterator
extends StreamingInitialRoundIterator<SGDObjectiveTerm>
    Iterate over all the terms that come up from grounding. On this first iteration, we will build the term cache up from ground rules and flush the terms to disk.
